# Distribution for Windows CommonsBase_GNU

## Objects and Assets

  $ get-object CommonsBase_GNU.Toolchain.W64dev@2.5.0 -s Release.Windows_x86 -f ${RUNTIME}/Windows_x86-Toolchain.W64dev-2.5.0.zip
  \test(pass)\dkobjects\;{
    "Release.Windows_x86": "o64gbxfsm7x4ufyqzfo7eyyxvnxpg575re46vcoqgbyy6knnhnskq"
  }

## GNU Awk

Use the wrapper package `CommonsBase_GNU.Awk@5.3.1` for native
Windows `Release.Windows_x86_64`, `Release.Windows_x86`, and
`Release.Windows_arm64` slots. The Windows package installs `bin/awk.exe`,
`bin/gawk.exe`, and `include/gawkapi.h`.

Validated extraction commands:

  $ get-object CommonsBase_GNU.Awk@5.3.1 -s Release.Windows_x86_64 -d ${RUNTIME}/Windows_x86_64-Awk-5.3.1
  \test(pass)\dkobjects\;{
    "Release.Windows_x86_64": "oaxv73eglv5t6rkbrqc7j5g6p7mrzzdeixxjuwj4ikzk32rfzm3ra"
  }
  $ get-object CommonsBase_GNU.Awk@5.3.1 -s Release.Windows_arm64 -d ${RUNTIME}/Windows_arm64-Awk-5.3.1
  \test(pass)\dkobjects\;{
    "Release.Windows_arm64": "o2ystozhbcxhzsqj5mih37eamoytkaviv7toqrgqzeiuosnxekd6a"
  }

## Bison

`CommonsBase_GNU.Bison@3.8.2` provides native Windows
`Release.Windows_x86_64`, `Release.Windows_x86`, and
`Release.Windows_arm64` slots. The repaired package installs `bison.exe`,
`yacc.cmd`, `liby.a`, and the support files under `share/`.

Validated extraction commands:

  $ get-object CommonsBase_GNU.Bison@3.8.2 -s Release.Windows_x86_64 -d ${RUNTIME}/Windows_x86_64-Bison-3.8.2
  \test(pass)\dkobjects\;{
